===============================================================================
-->
<!ELEMENT bconn EMPTY>
<!ATTLIST bconn nid CDATA #REQUIRED id CDATA #REQUIRED pr CDATA #IMPLIED sp CDATA #IMPLIED rt CDATA #IMPLIED ct CDATA #IMPLIED cs CDATA #IMPLIED>

<!--
===============================================================================
